'''克雷伯·德·曼東沙·瓦斯康塞洛斯·費侯'''（{{lang-pt|Kleber de Mendonça Vasconcellos Filho}}）是巴西電影導演、編劇、製片與影評人。<ref>{{cite web|title=Kleber Mendonça Filho|url=http://www.filmeb.com.br/quem-e-quem/diretor/kleber-mendonca-filho|website=Filme B|accessdate=25 August 2015|language=pt|archive-date=2016-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424110438/http://www.filmeb.com.br/quem-e-quem/diretor/kleber-mendonca-filho|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
克雷伯·曼東沙·費侯自新聞系畢業後，他先擔任影評與記者。<ref>{{cite web|title=Revista Continente|last1=Mendonça Filho|first1=Kleber|url=http://www.revistacontinente.com.br/|website=Revista Continente|accessdate=25 August 2015|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106210143/https://www.revistacontinente.com.br/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cinetica|last1=Mendonça Filho|first1=Kleber|url=http://revistacinetica.com.br/home/|website=Revista Cinetica|accessdate=25 August 2015|archive-date=2017-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170426003200/http://revistacinetica.com.br/home/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1990年代，他開始嘗試執導紀錄片、劇情片與攝像作品，他於2000年代從錄像轉投入數位與35釐米影片的拍攝，拍攝了許多短片。

2013年，他完成第一部劇情長片《{{link-pt|鄰居的狗吠聲|O Som ao Redor}}》，於[[鹿特丹影展|鹿特丹影展]]首映後便獲得許多影評讚賞，[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]影評人A. O. Scott將其列入他2012年十大佳片名單；本片也代表巴西角逐奧斯卡最佳外語片，但未獲提名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/brazil-sends-neighboring-sounds-to-oscars-1200654580/|title=Brazil Sends ‘Neighboring Sounds’ to Oscars|accessdate=September 20, 2013|work=Variety|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206171552/https://variety.com/2013/film/news/brazil-sends-neighboring-sounds-to-oscars-1200654580/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Brazil">{{cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/130920/brazil-picks-o-som-ao-redor-oscars-entry |title=Brazil picks "O Som ao Redor" as Oscars entry |accessdate=2013-09-21 |work=Global Post |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922134124/http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/afp/130920/brazil-picks-o-som-ao-redor-oscars-entry |archivedate=2013-09-22 }}</ref> 

2016年，克雷伯·曼東沙·費侯執導的第二部長片《{{link-en|水瓶女人心|Aquarius (film)}}》獲選為[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]正式競賽片<ref name="IW">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/cannes-live-stream-2016-film-festival-lineup-list |title=2016 Cannes Film Festival Announces Lineup |accessdate=14 April 2016 |work=IndieWire |archive-date=2016-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520032842/http://www.indiewire.com/article/cannes-live-stream-2016-film-festival-lineup-list |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="VarCannes">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-official-selection-lineup-2016-1201753269/ |title=Cannes 2016: Film Festival Unveils Official Selection Lineup |accessdate=14 April 2016 |work=Variety |archive-date=2016-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160901082634/http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-official-selection-lineup-2016-1201753269/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2019年，他與長期合作的製作設計Juliano Dornelles共同執導的《{{link-en|殺戮荒村|Bacurau}}》讓他第二次進入[[第72屆坎城影展|坎城影展]]正式競賽單元<ref name="Films2019">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2019/apr/18/cannes-festival-2019-full-list-of-films |title=Cannes festival 2019: full list of films |work=The Guardian |accessdate=2019-04-18 |archive-date=2019-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531171650/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2019/apr/18/cannes-festival-2019-full-list-of-films |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並獲得[[坎城影展評審團獎|評審團獎]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/cannes-film-festival-2019-winners-1203225973/ |title=Bong Joon-ho's ''Parasite'' Wins the Palme d'Or at Cannes |work=Variety |accessdate=26 May 2019 |archive-date=2019-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605043110/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/cannes-film-festival-2019-winners-1203225973/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

